"Yeah were going to Earth. It is really important to our history. 
Without it, none of us should hypothetically be around," he is met 
with an agreement by Strafe, "Unh-huh". Lightspeed continues, "and 
the Council believes the Decepticons are trying a movement there, and 
we thought we saw the last of them when we defeated them in 2010" he 
said, still following Jet V.  Strafe was getting bored by this 
however, and agreed "unh-hun" but left the base. He jumped up into 
the air, and transformed into his cruiser mode, and blasted off 
towards the exit, to explore the skies, and maybe hook up with the 
other Technobots.
